== 伸延閱讀 ==
* ''William Shatner and the Fromage Frontier'', eight-page interview by Claire Connors, seven photos including [https://archive.is/20130705150815/http://more-shatner.livejournal.com/370951.html cover] by Jeff Lipsky. ''[https://web.archive.org/web/20130822020220/http://cheeseconnoisseur.com/HOME.html Cheese Connoisseur]'', summer 2013, cover story, pages 26–33. Published by Phoenix Media Network, Inc., Boca Raton, Florida. Shatner discusses his career, health, current and future projects, and, especially, his appreciation for cheese.

